<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You've been invited to Deckard Inquiry Tool</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #004494;
        }
        .link-text {
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #0056b3;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .expiration-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #0056b3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #e7f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0056b3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Deckard Inquiry Tool</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
            Hello {{ invitation.firstName }} {{ invitation.lastName }},
        </div>

        <div class="message">
            <p>You've been invited to join the <strong>Deckard Inquiry Tool</strong> platform.</p>

            <p>This powerful tool allows you to manage inquiries, track orders, and streamline your communication with Deckard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>Your Account Details:</strong><br>
            Email: {{ invitation.email }}
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ registrationUrl }}" class="cta-button">Set Your Password & Get Started</a>
        </p>

        <div class="expiration-notice">
            <strong>⏰ Action Required:</strong><br>
            This invitation link will expire in <strong>{{ expirationDays }} day{{ expirationDays > 1 ? 's' : '' }}</strong>.
            Please complete your registration before {{ invitation.expiresAt|date('F j, Y \\a\\t g:i A') }}.
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px;">
            If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
        </p>

        <div class="link-text">
            {{ registrationUrl }}
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d;">
            <strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
            If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Deckard & Co GmbH. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
            This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.<br>
            If you did not expect this invitation, please ignore this email.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
